# Shuify - Isometric Room Planner

![alt text](<Screenshot 2025-12-15 134442-2.png>)
![alt text](room-recording.gif)

## Overview
A web application that allows users to design and arrange rooms in isometric 3D view with intuitive drag-and-drop functionality.

